WEBVTT

00:03:58.673 --> 00:04:01.458
so that those of us falling sick in prison

00:04:01.482 --> 00:04:04.355
would not necessarily
have to die in indignity.

00:04:05.950 --> 00:04:08.164
Having met Alexander,

00:04:08.188 --> 00:04:09.347
I had a chance,

00:04:09.371 --> 00:04:12.783
and he gave me the opportunity
and the support,

00:04:12.807 --> 00:04:16.112
to enroll for a university degree
at the University of London.

00:04:16.958 --> 00:04:19.339
Just like Mandela
studied from South Africa,

00:04:19.363 --> 00:04:22.601
I had a chance to study
at Kamiti Maximum Security Prison.

00:04:23.498 --> 00:04:25.164
And two years later,

00:04:25.188 --> 00:04:27.696
I became the first graduate of the program

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:31.204
from the University of London
from within the prison system.